---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { getSortedPosts } from '../utils/posts';

const posts = await getSortedPosts();
---

<Layout title="Earl's Place | Home">
    <section class="intro-text">
        <p>Below is a compilation of most but certainly not all of my trip reports. Missing are most fishing trips to area lakes, rivers and I almost never discuss coastal fishing. My fishing locations along the Texas coast are private unless it is a generic location. This is a lesson learned from many years ago when I was a teenager living on a Texas coastal barrier island. If I told you where I fished, good chance it was a lie, will even lie to my dad about where I fish.</p>

        <p>These reports are to provide myself, family and friends memories of good times and also to aid in the recall of details we may have forgotten so they can be referenced for future trips.</p>

        <p>
            <a href="posts/river-outfitters">River Outfitters</a>
            <a href="https://sites.google.com/site/earlatnipsplace/river-gages">River Gages</a>
            <a href="http://www.ozarkpages.com/cgi-bin/stages.pl?ST=level">Ozark Creek Summary</a>
        </p>

        <p>
            <a href="https://share.garmin.com/EarlAtnip">Where is Earl?</a>
            <a href="posts/earls-bucket-list">Earl's Bucket List</a>
            <a href="posts/special-photos">Special Photos</a>
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="post-list">
        <h2>Posts</h2>
		<ul>
			{posts.map((post) => (
				<li class="post-item">
					<a href={`posts/${post.slug}/`} class="post-title">
						<h3>{post.data.title}</h3>
					</a>
					<p class="post-description">{post.data.description}</p>
				</li>
			))}
		</ul>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
    .intro-text {
        margin-bottom: 2rem; /* Adds a 2rem margin to the bottom of the intro text section */
    }
    .intro-text p {
        margin-bottom: 1rem; /* Adds a 1rem margin to the bottom of each paragraph in the intro text */
        line-height: 1.6; /* Sets the line height for paragraphs in the intro text to 1.6 */
    }
    .intro-text a {
        margin-right: 1rem; /* Adds a 1rem margin to the right of each link in the intro text */
        text-decoration: none; /* Removes the underline from links */
        color: #007bff; /* Sets the link color to a shade of blue */
    }
    .intro-text a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline; /* Adds an underline to links when hovered over */
    }

	.post-list h2 {
		font-size: 1.5rem; /* Sets the font size of the h2 element in the post list to 1.5rem */
		font-weight: 500; /* Sets the font weight of the h2 element in the post list to 500 */
		margin-bottom: 2rem; /* Adds a 2rem margin to the bottom of the h2 element in the post list */
		text-align: center; /* Centers the h2 element in the post list */
		color: #666; /* Sets the color of the h2 element in the post list to a shade of gray */
	}
	.post-list ul {
		list-style: none; /* Removes the default list styling (e.g., bullet points) */
		padding: 0; /* Removes padding from the unordered list */
		margin: 0; /* Removes margin from the unordered list */
	}
	.post-item {
		margin-bottom: 2rem; /* Adds a 2rem margin to the bottom of each post item */
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light); /* Adds a light-colored border to the bottom of each post item */
		padding-bottom: 2rem; /* Adds 2rem of padding to the bottom of each post item */
	}
	.post-item:last-child {
		border-bottom: none; /* Removes the bottom border from the last post item */
		margin-bottom: 0; /* Removes the bottom margin from the last post item */
	}
	.post-title {
		text-decoration: none; /* Removes the underline from the post title */
	}
	.post-title h3 {
		color: var(--accent-maroon); /* Sets the color of the h3 element within the post title to a maroon accent color */
		margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0; /* Sets the margins of the h3 element within the post title */
		font-size: 1.4rem; /* Sets the font size of the h3 element within the post title to 1.4rem */
		font-weight: 600; /* Sets the font weight of the h3 element within the post title to 600 */
		transition: color 0.2s ease-in-out; /* Adds a smooth color transition effect to the h3 element */
	}
	.post-title:hover h3 {
		color: #000; /* Changes the color of the h3 element to black when the post title is hovered over */
	}
	.post-description {
		margin: 0; /* Removes the margin from the post description */
		line-height: 1.6; /* Sets the line height of the post description to 1.6 */
		color: #555; /* Sets the color of the post description to a shade of gray */
	}
</style>
